Benar?

110
00:07:49,093 --> 00:07:51,429
Jadi, tidak apa-apa kan?

111
00:07:53,097 --> 00:07:54,390
Ayo masuk ke dalam?

112
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,766
Baiklah.

113
